high_descs: Walk straight towards the microwave on the counter.
Open the left cabinet to the top of the microwave and take out the cup inside of it.
Bring the cup down in front of the microwave.
Open the microwave, heat up the cup, and take it out of the microwave.
Turn around and head towards the coffee maker on the counter.
Place the cup on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed cup on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Go to the cabinet above the microwave.
Take the mug from the cabinet.
Place the mug in the microwave.
Heat the mug in the microwave.
Go to the counter behind you.
Place the mug in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated mug in the coffee maker.

high_descs: Pick up the mug from the cabinet above the microwave.
Bring the mug to the microwave.
Heat the mug in the microwave.
Bring the mug to the coffee machine
Put the mug on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug on the coffee machine.
